content:
**Ahoy Sailors, here is the last week of changes. 9/7 - 9/11
We were happy with the release of the lobby and pleased with the feedback received overall. **

fields.name: Prisons "weekend" wrap up
fields.value: - Thank you for joining us for the free prisons weekend

fields.name: Lifeboat City
fields.value: - Removed buggy interactions between busses and mounts to prevent flying bug

fields.name: Lobby
fields.value:
- Cleaned up floating blocks 
- Filled obvious holes

fields.name: CTF
fields.value: - Pulled next match npc out of the ground and put him back on his pedestal

fields.name: Commands
fields.value: - Adding smart filtering to user commands to reduce latency and shenanigans
